 reach Necrosan. If the player were to beat Necrosan then they would get an ending. Only one cabinet of the game is known to exist, and it can be found at the Galloping Ghost Arcade in Brookfield, Illinois.\n\nAs of 02/11/2017, the emulation of the game is fully functional, thanks to YouTube user GruntZilla94.","url":"https://www.igdb.com/games/primal-rage-ii","videos":[{"id":54419,"video_id":"AwmBrWDcWZE"}],"websites":[{"id":218184,"url":"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Primal_Rage","type":{"id":3,"type":"Wikipedia"}},{"id":218183,"url":"https://primalrage.fandom.com/wiki/Primal_Rage_II","type":{"id":2,"type":"Community Wiki"}}]}